photo.caption: The Real Thalassery kaipola. Rich sweet snack made with egg, banana, dry fruits.. Sweet lovers should not skip this one..
Delicious Chattipathiri with original Thalassery recipe....Yummy made of meat and scrambled egg placed between four layers of edible sheet.
Erachipetty ... Soft snack.. meat masala covered with a sheet made of egg and milk.. Also added some malli leaf on the top for a different flavour blend.
Celebrate special Carribean cocktail.. Shake made of more than two fruits with ice cream... Really a Thick shake...
Classic unnakai made of banana paste with coconut and dry fruit filling inside... A Malabar bounty....
Erachipathiri made of meat masala beautifully sealed inside... You will definitely love it with a cup of hot sulaimani..
Spicy Falafel will not disappoint a vegan who love spices.. Veg masala layered between self cooked bread and sealed with a tomato slice...
